org.springframework.beans.factory.xml.BeanDefinitionParser
public class ExtraGatePluginBeanDefinitionParser
extends org.springframework.beans.factory.xml.AbstractSingleBeanDefinitionParser

Bean definition parser for <gate:extra-plugin>path</gate:extra-plugin> producing the equivalent of 

 <bean class="gate.util.spring.ExtraGatePlugin">
   <property name="location" value="path" />
 </bean>
While the element can take an id it is not normally necessary to provide one as the Init bean enumerates all ExtraGatePlugin beans by type, ignoring their IDs.
